WEBVTT

01:43.000 --> 01:46.030
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.140 --> 01:49.000
[Episode 34]

01:55.150 --> 01:55.890
Yue!

01:56.229 --> 01:57.020
Captain Jiang!

01:57.600 --> 01:58.440
Yue!

02:00.030 --> 02:01.960
Yiming, call 911!

02:02.390 --> 02:03.430
Hurry up. Call 911!

02:03.510 --> 02:04.070
Hurry!

02:09.630 --> 02:10.400
Rescue center?

02:10.430 --> 02:11.070
Someone's injured here.

02:11.110 --> 02:12.500
Please send an ambulance.

02:16.600 --> 02:19.810
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

02:33.310 --> 02:34.270
Mom,

02:34.950 --> 02:37.079
the weather is great today.

02:38.030 --> 02:39.390
I really want to show you.

02:49.470 --> 02:50.130
Lu Yan.

02:51.150 --> 02:52.750
Emergency department just got a call.

02:52.829 --> 02:53.870
Several police officers were injured

02:53.870 --> 02:55.050
in an explosion while on duty.

02:55.070 --> 02:56.010
They're being sent over.

02:56.590 --> 02:57.350
Police?

03:04.890 --> 03:11.430
[Emergency Department]

03:15.460 --> 03:16.270
What happened?

03:16.310 --> 03:17.579
There was an explosion in the western suburbs.

03:17.600 --> 03:19.150
Two policemen are unconscious.

03:20.470 --> 03:21.210
Be careful.

03:21.230 --> 03:21.990
Be careful.

03:23.710 --> 03:24.870
Qin Yue!

04:03.270 --> 04:03.800
Hurry!

04:03.830 --> 04:04.640
Inform the operating room.

04:04.670 --> 04:05.630
for immediate surgery.

04:06.030 --> 04:07.390
The patient is unconscious and unresponsive.

04:08.710 --> 04:10.210
Equal and round pupils in both eyes.

04:10.270 --> 04:11.410
Sensitive to light reflex.

04:11.510 --> 04:12.930
Multiple burn wounds on the back, external injuries.

04:13.030 --> 04:14.430
Hemorrhagic shock cannot be ruled out.

04:17.170 --> 04:18.660
Blood pressure is 86 over 50.

04:19.149 --> 04:20.250
Heart rate 130.

04:20.410 --> 04:21.320
Blood oxygen 95.

04:21.870 --> 04:22.550
Full-speed replenishment.

04:22.590 --> 04:23.430
Notify the blood bank to prepare blood.

04:23.430 --> 04:24.700
Prepare red blood cells and plasma.

04:26.280 --> 04:27.520
Central venous catheterization.

05:19.630 --> 05:20.480
Liu Hao.

05:21.500 --> 05:22.440
Director Xing.

05:22.670 --> 05:24.020
How is it going?

05:24.230 --> 05:25.790
Captain Jiang is in the ward now.

05:25.810 --> 05:27.180
Qin Yue is still in surgery.

05:28.580 --> 05:29.380
Dr. Lu.

05:31.080 --> 05:31.860
Doctor.

05:31.970 --> 05:32.790
We've conducted

05:32.790 --> 05:33.790
a systematic check on Captain Jiang.

05:33.950 --> 05:35.030
Currently, it appears to be

05:35.070 --> 05:36.730
massive bleeding caused by external injuries.

05:36.830 --> 05:38.530
Fortunately, he's physically strong.

05:38.790 --> 05:39.670
There's no

05:39.670 --> 05:40.800
life danger for now.

05:41.340 --> 05:42.150
When will he

05:42.190 --> 05:42.870
wake up?

05:43.030 --> 05:44.450
It's just a minor concussion.

05:44.590 --> 05:45.240
Don't worry.

05:45.270 --> 05:46.310
Nothing serious.

05:46.600 --> 05:47.310
Okay.

05:47.750 --> 05:48.360
Doctor,

05:48.680 --> 05:49.860
please

05:50.040 --> 05:50.630
take good care of

05:50.680 --> 05:51.540
them.

05:52.470 --> 05:53.130
Okay.

05:53.150 --> 05:53.590
Come.

05:53.590 --> 05:54.380
Lu.

05:55.050 --> 05:55.750
Don't worry.

05:55.830 --> 05:56.710
Leave Auntie to me.

05:57.270 --> 05:58.580
Thank you, Qiao Rui.

05:59.260 --> 06:00.080
I'll go first.

06:01.350 --> 06:05.830
[Outpatient]

06:06.710 --> 06:07.520
Doctor.

06:07.980 --> 06:08.980
How is it?

06:10.070 --> 06:11.080
The surgery went well.

06:11.190 --> 06:12.190
The rebar that pierced the lower leg

06:12.190 --> 06:13.160
has been removed.

06:13.190 --> 06:14.090
No damage to muscles or bones.

06:14.710 --> 06:15.470
But the patient

06:15.470 --> 06:16.520
is now in shock

06:16.550 --> 06:17.950
due to excessive blood loss.

06:18.000 --> 06:19.110
We will do our best

06:19.110 --> 06:20.150
to treat him.

06:20.470 --> 06:21.160
Don't worry.

06:21.560 --> 06:22.920
Okay, thank you, doctor.

06:22.950 --> 06:23.510
Thank you.

06:23.750 --> 06:24.450
Thank you.

06:24.610 --> 06:25.370
Thank you.

06:29.930 --> 06:30.680
Liu Hao.

06:31.350 --> 06:32.860
How is the situation in Wenchang Village?

06:33.380 --> 06:33.909
The technical department

06:33.950 --> 06:35.230
has already surveyed the scene.

06:35.310 --> 06:36.390
It was a dust explosion

06:36.480 --> 06:37.700
caused by an electrical fire.

06:38.630 --> 06:39.950
So Wen Peng

06:40.070 --> 06:41.390
deliberately leaked his whereabouts

06:41.500 --> 06:43.130
and set this trap beforehand.

06:43.550 --> 06:44.200
That's right.

06:44.340 --> 06:45.790
Luckily Captain Jiang arrived in time

06:45.830 --> 06:46.750
and saved Qin Yue.

06:47.659 --> 06:49.350
Contact the Western Suburbs Branch immediately

06:49.470 --> 06:51.630
to inspect all streets and exits

06:51.659 --> 06:52.890
within 10 kilometers of Wenchang Village.

06:53.550 --> 06:54.150
Also,

06:54.710 --> 06:55.850
have the surveillance center

06:55.950 --> 06:57.000
search for Wen Peng's traces

06:57.550 --> 06:58.880
through the Skynet system.

06:59.070 --> 06:59.750
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

07:29.670 --> 07:31.740
Isn't your mission quite dangerous?

07:33.470 --> 07:34.580
I'm much better now.

07:34.710 --> 07:35.470
But there's always

07:35.470 --> 07:36.540
some level of risk.

07:36.710 --> 07:38.340
Since it's so dangerous,

07:38.909 --> 07:41.220
have you ever thought about changing

07:41.470 --> 07:42.360
your job?

07:42.630 --> 07:43.190
I...

07:43.270 --> 07:43.990
Mom.

07:44.010 --> 07:46.110
What are you talking about?

07:46.470 --> 07:48.100
He's doing well

07:48.130 --> 07:49.300
as a police.

07:49.409 --> 07:50.970
Why would he change his job?

08:15.720 --> 08:16.700
You must be worried.

08:23.870 --> 08:24.720
I'm fine.

08:27.510 --> 08:28.740
Don't worry.

08:30.110 --> 08:31.460
How can I not worry?

08:33.630 --> 08:34.710
You're fine? You...

08:36.070 --> 08:36.630
Your

08:38.830 --> 08:40.460
arm was blown up.

08:41.990 --> 08:43.130
Don't worry.

08:44.480 --> 08:45.620
I'm really fine.

08:45.650 --> 08:46.590
Don't worry.

08:52.730 --> 08:54.080
There won't be a next time.

08:54.550 --> 08:55.710
Next time?

08:56.780 --> 08:57.850
I'm scared.

09:05.170 --> 09:06.400
Jiang Chengyi,

09:10.640 --> 09:12.010
don't get hurt again.

09:13.700 --> 09:14.840
I can't live without you.

09:17.950 --> 09:18.730
Alright.

09:19.120 --> 09:20.000
Don't worry.

09:25.760 --> 09:27.420
Can you help me up?

09:28.190 --> 09:28.790
Why?

09:30.510 --> 09:31.470
Help me up.

09:31.510 --> 09:32.630
I need to use the restroom.

09:32.910 --> 09:33.980
Restroom?

09:34.390 --> 09:35.030
Come.

09:43.430 --> 09:44.580
Don't be angry.

09:46.240 --> 09:47.150
I'm fine.

09:47.880 --> 09:49.030
You're really...

09:50.670 --> 09:51.480
Don't be angry.

09:52.350 --> 09:52.830
Okay.

10:37.690 --> 10:40.580
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

10:40.710 --> 10:41.940
Director Xing has ordered

10:42.030 --> 10:43.240
to set up checkpoints at every intersection

10:43.310 --> 10:44.130
in Ninghai City

10:44.350 --> 10:46.030
to inspect vehicles and pedestrians

10:46.230 --> 10:47.230
in case Wen Peng escapes.

10:51.470 --> 10:52.560
Qin Yue's...

10:53.200 --> 10:54.110
badly injured.

10:54.150 --> 10:55.360
How's his mental state?

10:57.620 --> 10:58.860
He just feels guilty,

10:59.070 --> 11:00.600
saying he shouldn't have acted on his own

11:00.910 --> 11:01.590
and involved you.

11:03.080 --> 11:04.210
I'm not talking about that.

11:05.510 --> 11:08.000
You know how lively he usually is.

11:08.940 --> 11:10.620
With such a severe leg injury,

11:10.900 --> 11:12.270
I'm afraid he'll feel bad.

11:13.750 --> 11:14.990
He was just teasing with the nurse

11:15.060 --> 11:15.910
and kicked me out.

11:17.470 --> 11:18.150
That's good.

11:20.330 --> 11:21.320
-Lu Yan.
-Dr. Lu.

11:21.670 --> 11:22.870
Captain Jiang, I'll go check on Qin Yue.

11:22.890 --> 11:23.570
Okay.

11:24.030 --> 11:24.790
You're leaving.

11:24.810 --> 11:25.580
You guys talk.

11:28.230 --> 11:29.340
Give me a hug.

11:29.750 --> 11:31.080
How are you?

11:34.590 --> 11:35.980
I think...

11:38.150 --> 11:39.710
I think I can be discharged.

11:40.430 --> 11:41.380
Discharged?

11:41.710 --> 11:42.310
No way.

11:42.710 --> 11:43.430
You should wait

11:43.470 --> 11:45.000
at least another two days.

11:44.560 --> 11:45.910
♫As the city flickers♫

11:45.830 --> 11:47.480
These are just minor injuries,

11:47.260 --> 11:50.140
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

11:47.630 --> 11:48.720
and I have a lot of things

11:48.740 --> 11:49.630
to take care of.

11:51.050 --> 11:52.750
What about the follow-up appointment

11:51.320 --> 11:52.610
♫And you, who love to smile♫

11:52.790 --> 11:53.430
this afternoon?

11:53.630 --> 11:56.330
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

11:55.270 --> 11:56.000
How about this?

11:56.230 --> 11:57.300
Let me be discharged

11:57.120 --> 11:59.660
♫The humor of time♫

11:57.390 --> 11:59.730
and I'll come back to change the dressing on time

12:00.190 --> 12:01.540
and do all the follow-ups you arranged.

12:00.950 --> 12:03.450
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

12:01.590 --> 12:02.300
Okay.

12:04.190 --> 12:05.120
Then you...

12:04.470 --> 12:10.330
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

12:06.430 --> 12:07.640
do it this afternoon.

12:11.600 --> 12:13.300
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

12:12.830 --> 12:13.800
If you're not busy,

12:13.900 --> 12:15.050
sit with me for a while.

12:14.330 --> 12:17.370
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

12:18.480 --> 12:19.910
♫The stubborn me♫

12:19.400 --> 12:21.080
Have you eaten?

12:21.140 --> 12:23.840
♫I always think of the far future♫

12:22.490 --> 12:27.830
[Public Security of the New era]

12:22.560 --> 12:23.910
So, you think

12:24.670 --> 12:25.710
Wen Peng is likely

12:25.750 --> 12:26.550
to commit more crimes?

12:26.960 --> 12:27.710
Yes, Director Xing.

12:28.070 --> 12:30.130
Wen Peng's initial motive

12:30.270 --> 12:31.870
was to separate Lu Yan

12:31.870 --> 12:33.070
and Jiang Chengyi by hurting people

12:33.090 --> 12:34.320
around them.

12:35.150 --> 12:36.750
But with this dust explosion,

12:36.780 --> 12:37.430
his attitude

12:37.430 --> 12:38.890
has completely changed.

12:39.430 --> 12:40.290
Wen Peng has been plotting

12:40.350 --> 12:41.260
for years,

12:41.470 --> 12:42.510
and in the end, not only

12:42.550 --> 12:43.450
did he not get Lu Yan,

12:43.470 --> 12:45.340
but he also ruined himself.

12:45.830 --> 12:47.150
He must blame all problems

12:47.170 --> 12:48.990
on Jiang Chengyi.

12:49.670 --> 12:50.740
So, I'm certain

12:50.870 --> 12:52.680
he will make another move against Jiang Chengyi.

12:54.990 --> 12:56.160
Jiang should be

12:57.590 --> 12:58.930
more aware of Wen Peng's

12:59.070 --> 13:00.400
criminal motives than we are.

13:01.700 --> 13:02.430
In that case,

13:02.950 --> 13:04.440
you should find time to visit him,

13:04.970 --> 13:06.230
offer some proper

13:06.270 --> 13:07.430
care and reminders.

13:07.760 --> 13:08.640
Yes, Director Xing.

13:17.710 --> 13:18.830
How did you drive?

13:19.470 --> 13:20.400
Look over there.

13:20.710 --> 13:22.010
Why did you suddenly change the route?

13:22.270 --> 13:23.340
Get off. Get off.

13:23.710 --> 13:25.110
Get off to solve this. Get off!

13:27.010 --> 13:28.280
Get off!

13:30.730 --> 13:31.470
Get off!

13:33.170 --> 13:34.110
Do you hear me?

13:34.760 --> 13:35.610
What are you shouting for?

13:36.110 --> 13:36.980
What's going on?

13:37.870 --> 13:38.740
Officer,

13:38.770 --> 13:39.790
I was driving normally.

13:39.830 --> 13:40.750
How did he drive?

13:49.580 --> 13:50.630
Please show me your driving license

13:50.630 --> 13:51.380
and vehicle registration certificate.

14:04.520 --> 14:05.540
What's your name?

14:08.620 --> 14:09.440
Wen Peng.

14:15.970 --> 14:17.460
Please turn off the engine and get off.

14:29.150 --> 14:30.270
Mr. Wen,

14:30.730 --> 14:32.070
please turn off the engine and get off.

14:39.130 --> 14:39.690
Stop!

14:43.670 --> 14:44.660
Command center. Command center.

14:44.740 --> 14:45.440
This is Ninghai

14:45.470 --> 14:46.490
Anshan Traffic Brigade.

14:46.520 --> 14:48.630
I just spotted the wanted

14:48.660 --> 14:50.230
criminal Wen Peng on Haining Road.

14:50.310 --> 14:51.430
He was wearing a black baseball cap,

14:51.500 --> 14:52.590
a black hoodie,

14:52.670 --> 14:53.310
and driving a black

14:53.350 --> 14:54.230
Great Wall SUV

14:54.350 --> 14:56.230
with the license plate number Pu AH530A.

14:56.360 --> 14:57.860
He's fleeing towards Youyi Road.

14:57.890 --> 14:58.740
Requesting backup.

15:16.620 --> 15:17.430
I knew Wen Peng

15:17.470 --> 15:19.100
wouldn't give up easily.

15:19.740 --> 15:20.390
I've told Lu Yan

15:20.430 --> 15:21.310
and Zhong

15:21.330 --> 15:22.290
to be

15:22.590 --> 15:23.510
careful recently.

15:24.150 --> 15:24.630
Yes.

15:24.650 --> 15:25.920
Be careful.

15:27.240 --> 15:27.910
By the way,

15:28.340 --> 15:29.140
Yu Bofeng

15:29.990 --> 15:32.070
asked me to apologize to you.

15:32.870 --> 15:34.510
He said he realized

15:34.670 --> 15:35.830
he was used by Wen Peng.

15:39.700 --> 15:41.090
You two...

15:42.170 --> 15:43.550
are back in touch?

15:45.600 --> 15:48.160
We just added each other on WeChat.

15:48.360 --> 15:49.720
Nothing much.

15:52.580 --> 15:53.510
That's good.

15:53.550 --> 15:54.720
Good.

15:55.310 --> 15:56.910
Well, I just think

15:56.950 --> 15:58.700
it's not easy for him

15:58.850 --> 16:00.380
to go from being

16:00.790 --> 16:01.910
a big star to this.

16:03.130 --> 16:04.340
You feel sorry for him.

16:04.620 --> 16:06.190
No, I'm not.

16:06.230 --> 16:07.750
Stop talking nonsense.

16:10.510 --> 16:10.960
Captain Jiang,

16:11.030 --> 16:11.830
Wen Peng was just spotted

16:11.870 --> 16:12.630
on Haining Road.

16:13.110 --> 16:14.230
Has it been confirmed?

16:14.470 --> 16:15.310
The traffic police compared

16:15.310 --> 16:15.710
his ID.

16:15.790 --> 16:16.410
It's Wen Peng.

16:16.500 --> 16:17.630
Sihan and Li Yong are already on their way.

16:19.360 --> 16:20.410
Tell them

16:20.790 --> 16:21.900
we'll be there soon.

16:22.190 --> 16:22.630
Yes.

16:23.670 --> 16:24.830
What, are you going too?

16:24.870 --> 16:25.350
I have to go.

16:25.430 --> 16:25.910
Take it easy.

16:26.030 --> 16:26.880
I'm fine.

17:03.210 --> 17:04.150
Something's up.

17:04.230 --> 17:05.750
I need to go out now.

17:07.550 --> 17:09.030
Be careful.

17:09.589 --> 17:10.319
Don't worry.

17:10.589 --> 17:11.700
I'll be back to change the dressing on time.

17:12.109 --> 17:12.589
I'm leaving.

17:40.100 --> 17:41.640
Calling Captain Jiang.

17:42.870 --> 17:43.460
Hello?

17:43.700 --> 17:44.430
The suspect is driving

17:44.460 --> 17:45.780
west on Jianshe Road.

17:45.810 --> 17:46.910
We're following him closely.

17:46.990 --> 17:47.570
Please give your order.

17:47.610 --> 17:48.090
I know.

17:49.100 --> 17:51.380
Make sure to intercept the suspect

17:51.400 --> 17:52.280
at the Heping Road fork

17:52.390 --> 17:53.840
to prevent him from escaping again.

17:54.270 --> 17:54.900
Copy that.

17:55.070 --> 17:55.620
Okay.

18:06.600 --> 18:07.590
[Public Security]

18:09.710 --> 18:10.800
-Police!
-Stop!

18:10.820 --> 18:11.520
Stop!

18:14.170 --> 18:14.890
Stop!

18:17.770 --> 18:18.390
Stop!

18:18.930 --> 18:19.610
Stop!

18:20.960 --> 18:21.600
Stop!

18:24.500 --> 18:25.210
Get up.

18:25.250 --> 18:25.960
Get up.

18:26.660 --> 18:27.620
Go. Behave yourself.

18:27.650 --> 18:28.510
Behave yourself!

18:28.830 --> 18:29.640
Hello, Captain Jiang.

18:29.670 --> 18:31.220
The suspect vehicle has been intercepted.

18:29.870 --> 18:33.310
[Public Security]

18:31.470 --> 18:32.270
We caught a suspect,

18:32.310 --> 18:33.310
but it's not Wen Peng.

18:33.450 --> 18:34.550
There were three people in the car,

18:34.570 --> 18:35.970
all dressed the same,

18:36.010 --> 18:37.720
running toward Wuzhou Home

18:37.790 --> 18:38.920
and Dayue City respectively

18:41.470 --> 18:42.940
Okay, I got it.

18:43.170 --> 18:44.480
Notify the surrounding police forces.

18:44.530 --> 18:45.750
Don't let him disguise again.

18:45.830 --> 18:46.690
Got it.

18:55.770 --> 18:58.900
[Emergency Department]

20:02.750 --> 20:03.350
Stop!

20:03.640 --> 20:04.320
Stop there!

20:11.150 --> 20:11.710
Stop there!

20:12.110 --> 20:12.820
Don't move!

20:13.760 --> 20:14.360
Don't move!

20:16.930 --> 20:17.720
Behave yourself.

20:22.480 --> 20:23.520
This one's a fake too.

20:25.170 --> 20:25.670
Hello?

20:26.550 --> 20:27.150
What?

20:27.580 --> 20:28.840
Okay, got it.

20:30.910 --> 20:32.310
Captain Jiang, we've caught the other one as well.

20:32.310 --> 20:33.350
It's not Wen Peng either.

20:35.350 --> 20:35.870
Get in.

20:36.550 --> 20:36.910
Let's go.

20:46.650 --> 20:47.530
Lu,

20:49.330 --> 20:50.030
are you going to

20:50.070 --> 20:51.270
stay with your mom tonight?

20:54.430 --> 20:55.270
With this non-stop schedule,

20:55.310 --> 20:56.550
can your body take it?

20:58.940 --> 20:59.880
I'm fine.

21:00.470 --> 21:01.410
I'm used to it.

21:05.230 --> 21:05.990
This is hot milk tea.

21:06.030 --> 21:06.630
Drink it

21:06.830 --> 21:07.760
to replenish some energy.

21:08.510 --> 21:10.420
Tell me if you need anything.

21:11.990 --> 21:12.940
Go back.

21:21.580 --> 21:22.750
I'm off work now.

21:22.790 --> 21:23.900
I'll be there in 30 minutes.

22:09.990 --> 22:10.710
You're off work?

22:16.120 --> 22:21.160
[Get Well Soon]

22:21.230 --> 22:31.650
[Patient Notice]

23:30.660 --> 23:31.100
You...

24:15.680 --> 24:16.710
Wait.

24:17.850 --> 24:18.550
Thank you.

24:30.350 --> 24:31.290
You have a patient?

24:34.570 --> 24:36.210
Which department are you from?

24:37.320 --> 24:38.510
I'm from General Surgery.

24:41.690 --> 24:42.940
Are you new here?

24:43.580 --> 24:44.410
Yes.

24:45.420 --> 24:46.920
No wonder I haven't seen you before.

25:01.350 --> 25:04.170
[Emergency]

25:11.610 --> 25:12.440
Captain Jiang.

25:12.540 --> 25:13.390
It's Wen Peng.

25:14.070 --> 25:14.470
Look.

25:14.490 --> 25:15.420
Can you zoom in?

25:19.230 --> 25:20.490
Where did he go after that?

25:22.340 --> 25:26.630
[Parking lot]

25:28.560 --> 25:32.150
[Parking lot]

25:33.510 --> 25:35.590
Track this car in the system

25:35.610 --> 25:36.570
and see where he went.

25:36.670 --> 25:37.030
Yes.

25:37.040 --> 25:37.580
Hurry.

25:41.610 --> 25:42.620
Matron Qiao,

25:44.770 --> 25:47.080
don't tell anyone

25:47.280 --> 25:48.320
about this.

25:48.590 --> 25:49.110
Okay.

25:49.130 --> 25:49.950
Thank you.

26:06.030 --> 26:06.720
Hello?

26:07.110 --> 26:10.390
[Under Construction. Do Not Enter]

26:07.190 --> 26:08.120
Hello, Captain Jiang.

26:08.670 --> 26:09.430
We found the black Buick

26:09.470 --> 26:10.650
that Wen Peng took Lu Yan in

26:10.710 --> 26:11.870
at the construction site on Wujiang Road

26:11.910 --> 26:12.830
in the Xincheng District.

26:13.040 --> 26:15.320
[Under Construction. Do Not Enter]

26:13.670 --> 26:14.230
And

26:14.270 --> 26:15.660
a construction vehicle is missing here.

26:15.910 --> 26:16.810
We suspect

26:16.870 --> 26:18.070
Wen Peng brought the car here

26:18.150 --> 26:18.510
to

26:18.510 --> 26:19.710
switch vehicles

26:19.830 --> 26:20.890
and evade our capture.

26:20.820 --> 26:22.480
[Under Construction. Do Not Enter]

26:20.990 --> 26:22.460
Someone must have helped Wen Peng escape.

26:22.590 --> 26:23.710
I've already asked others

26:23.790 --> 26:25.020
to track the construction vehicle.

26:25.110 --> 26:25.990
Okay, that's great.

26:26.010 --> 26:26.620
Keep investigating.

26:26.770 --> 26:27.490
Yes, Captain Jiang.

27:05.690 --> 27:06.760
You're awake.

27:13.070 --> 27:13.780
Wen Peng,

27:15.440 --> 27:16.860
what do you want?

27:17.150 --> 27:17.990
What do I want?

27:20.110 --> 27:21.070
Of course I want to

27:21.110 --> 27:22.000
be with you.

27:26.830 --> 27:28.310
Help!

27:28.320 --> 27:30.020
Is anyone there?

27:30.430 --> 27:32.350
Help!

27:33.500 --> 27:34.510
No one is here.

27:34.580 --> 27:36.130
It's just the two of us.

27:42.420 --> 27:44.290
I remember you once said

27:44.540 --> 27:45.590
the place you want to go most

27:45.630 --> 27:46.770
is Lake Baikal.

27:47.210 --> 27:48.260
But

27:48.710 --> 27:50.600
I can't take you there now.

27:52.230 --> 27:53.120
But

27:53.620 --> 27:55.200
when I bought this villa,

27:55.230 --> 27:56.290
I had already decided

27:57.230 --> 28:00.070
I want to spend the rest of my life

28:00.860 --> 28:02.250
with you.

28:10.760 --> 28:11.740
What do you think?

28:14.320 --> 28:15.210
Do you like it?

28:16.930 --> 28:17.870
You like it, don't you?

28:24.830 --> 28:26.390
You took me away.

28:27.500 --> 28:28.480
Jiang Chengyi and others

28:28.510 --> 28:29.760
will soon find out.

28:30.130 --> 28:31.630
All the police are after you now.

28:31.670 --> 28:32.790
You can't escape.

28:33.260 --> 28:35.210
I'm not escaping.

28:35.300 --> 28:36.730
Didn't I tell you just now?

28:37.270 --> 28:38.540
I want to be with you.

28:46.830 --> 28:47.930
I know

28:48.310 --> 28:49.830
you can't accept me now.

28:49.850 --> 28:50.490
But

28:50.670 --> 28:52.050
I can promise you

28:52.870 --> 28:54.660
as long as you are willing to be with me,

28:55.870 --> 28:56.590
you won't be hurt

28:56.640 --> 28:57.710
by anyone.

28:58.110 --> 28:58.870
From beginning to end,

28:58.910 --> 29:00.370
you're the only one who hurt me.

29:01.470 --> 29:02.390
You've hurt

29:02.390 --> 29:04.460
everyone closest to me.

29:06.720 --> 29:08.370
What do you really want?

29:09.070 --> 29:09.830
Why don't you understand

29:09.830 --> 29:11.450
why I did all this?

29:11.510 --> 29:13.980
I did all this for you.

29:14.510 --> 29:15.490
No one

29:15.710 --> 29:16.310
will ever

29:16.350 --> 29:17.310
love you the way I do.

29:17.310 --> 29:17.910
You know?

29:17.990 --> 29:18.750
Stop saying

29:18.750 --> 29:20.390
such disgusting words!

29:22.990 --> 29:24.450
So you're rejecting me?

29:24.550 --> 29:25.820
I'm not rejecting you.

29:27.750 --> 29:28.480
I hate you.

29:29.280 --> 29:30.360
I despise you.

29:33.670 --> 29:34.590
So you don't want

29:34.590 --> 29:35.790
to be with me, right?

29:39.320 --> 29:41.010
Even if none of this had happened,

29:41.410 --> 29:42.960
I wouldn't be with you.

29:45.840 --> 29:47.210
I hate you.

29:47.550 --> 29:48.190
The most regretful thing

29:48.210 --> 29:50.130
in my life is knowing you.

29:50.230 --> 29:51.980
I never should have saved you.

29:51.980 --> 29:53.160
I shouldn't have said...

29:53.160 --> 29:54.420
Enough!

30:02.980 --> 30:04.640
I'll go check if Auntie's awake.

30:06.100 --> 30:07.110
What are you doing?

30:07.140 --> 30:08.680
Didn't I tell you?

30:09.590 --> 30:11.230
As long as you agree to be with me,

30:11.310 --> 30:12.950
I'll do whatever you want me to do,

30:13.550 --> 30:14.310
including

30:16.230 --> 30:18.430
keep hurting the people you care the most.

30:18.800 --> 30:19.860
You...

30:20.320 --> 30:21.790
You've gone crazy.

30:59.440 --> 31:00.610
Lu Yan,

31:00.810 --> 31:01.670
do you know

31:01.790 --> 31:03.010
what day it is today?

31:11.370 --> 31:12.110
My birthday.

31:44.120 --> 31:45.430
When I was eight,

31:46.950 --> 31:48.120
my mother left me.

31:49.590 --> 31:51.400
After she left,

31:52.980 --> 31:54.520
I never celebrated my birthday again.

31:57.670 --> 31:58.390
Because

32:00.300 --> 32:01.940
every time it was my birthday,

32:02.360 --> 32:03.800
my dad would think of my mom

32:05.360 --> 32:07.010
and get extra angry.

32:08.080 --> 32:09.560
So I was especially

32:10.270 --> 32:11.430
envious of other kids.

32:13.370 --> 32:14.870
They had family and friends

32:14.910 --> 32:16.050
to celebrate their birthdays with them.

32:21.770 --> 32:23.090
But fortunately,

32:23.330 --> 32:24.290
you're here with me today.

32:27.290 --> 32:28.060
Lu Yan,

32:28.710 --> 32:30.150
do you like this cake?

32:30.570 --> 32:32.080
It's the same style my mom bought

32:32.100 --> 32:34.080
the first time she celebrated my birthday.

32:36.270 --> 32:36.990
Today,

32:38.350 --> 32:39.820
let's celebrate my birthday together, okay?

32:46.570 --> 32:47.550
Can you

32:47.590 --> 32:48.670
sing a birthday song for me?

32:52.600 --> 32:53.240
It's okay.

32:54.260 --> 32:55.470
If you won't sing, I'll sing.

32:56.960 --> 33:00.730
Happy birthday to me.

33:01.000 --> 33:04.470
Happy birthday to me.

33:04.750 --> 33:08.590
Happy birthday to me.

33:09.990 --> 33:14.990
Happy birthday to me.

33:23.220 --> 33:24.390
My wish is

33:25.130 --> 33:26.350
that we will

33:26.350 --> 33:27.750
always be together, just the two of us,

33:28.270 --> 33:29.660
forever and ever.

33:51.660 --> 33:52.970
Come on, take a bite.

33:54.010 --> 33:55.530
What's the point of you doing this?

33:55.630 --> 33:57.160
Of course, there's a point.

33:57.470 --> 33:58.510
Today is my birthday,

33:58.510 --> 33:59.270
and it's also

33:59.270 --> 34:00.020
our anniversary.

34:00.070 --> 34:00.550
How wonderful.

34:06.380 --> 34:07.800
You know it.

34:09.920 --> 34:11.230
I was forced.

34:16.889 --> 34:18.449
Do you have to

34:18.850 --> 34:20.000
make me unhappy

34:20.000 --> 34:20.949
on such a happy day?

34:23.760 --> 34:25.100
For the sake of my birthday,

34:27.630 --> 34:28.630
have a bite.

34:30.040 --> 34:31.000
Have a bite.

34:31.820 --> 34:32.489
Have a bite.

34:33.210 --> 34:34.050
Get up!

34:34.389 --> 34:35.380
Have a bite!

34:35.989 --> 34:37.230
Get up!

34:37.670 --> 34:38.560
Get up!

34:38.630 --> 34:40.020
Have a bite!

35:20.070 --> 35:20.470
Hello?

35:21.210 --> 35:21.930
You found it?

35:24.280 --> 35:25.570
Okay, got it.

35:29.390 --> 35:30.070
Captain Jiang.

35:30.100 --> 35:31.260
The construction vehicle has been found.

35:31.310 --> 35:32.510
Wen Peng drove from

35:32.550 --> 35:33.510
Xincheng District's Wujiang Road

35:33.550 --> 35:34.430
all the way south to the Laowan District's

35:34.450 --> 35:35.590
nature reserve on the national highway.

35:35.610 --> 35:37.090
The nature reserve is sparsely populated.

35:37.230 --> 35:37.830
There's a lot of traffic

35:37.830 --> 35:38.550
and no surveillance.

35:38.710 --> 35:39.920
I guess there are two possibilities.

35:40.430 --> 35:41.910
One is that he changed vehicles in the reserve.

35:41.950 --> 35:43.100
The other is that he went straight up the mountain.

35:45.020 --> 35:46.010
Send people to search.

35:46.220 --> 35:47.000
Okay.

35:47.860 --> 35:48.590
Hurry.

36:21.170 --> 36:22.030
Lu Yan.

36:24.200 --> 36:25.180
Lu Yan, are you alright?

36:25.260 --> 36:26.020
Lu Yan.

36:26.470 --> 36:27.190
Why did you fall down?

36:27.210 --> 36:27.940
Get up.

36:28.070 --> 36:28.760
One, two.

36:31.760 --> 36:32.910
Are you hurt?

36:33.510 --> 36:34.510
Are you okay? Let me see.

36:34.780 --> 36:35.300
Let me see.

36:39.020 --> 36:39.800
I'm sorry.

36:39.830 --> 36:40.830
I didn't take good care of you.

36:43.880 --> 36:45.330
But I have a surprise for you.

37:17.040 --> 37:17.890
Look.

37:18.050 --> 37:19.170
It's beautiful.

37:30.880 --> 37:32.240
Isn't it not allowed to set off fireworks?

37:32.270 --> 37:33.700
The fish ran away.

37:34.040 --> 37:34.910
Lu Yan,

37:35.280 --> 37:36.220
you know what?

37:37.490 --> 37:38.710
Today is the happiest day

37:38.750 --> 37:39.750
in my life.

37:41.760 --> 37:43.150
I feel that everything I've done

37:43.170 --> 37:44.110
for this day

37:44.110 --> 37:44.950
is so worth it.

37:54.720 --> 37:56.330
From the first day I met you,

37:57.110 --> 37:58.290
I've been imagining

37:59.140 --> 38:00.390
that we would have

38:00.870 --> 38:02.470
a cabin with a view of the lake.

38:04.310 --> 38:05.880
We would take walks together during the day,

38:06.740 --> 38:09.460
and read books together by the fireplace at night.

38:14.240 --> 38:15.220
This place

38:15.250 --> 38:17.230
is not as good as Lake Baikal,

38:17.380 --> 38:18.880
but it also fulfills my dream.

38:23.750 --> 38:24.640
In the future,

38:25.560 --> 38:26.430
I will definitely take you

38:26.430 --> 38:27.260
to see Lake Baikal.

38:28.870 --> 38:30.240
Not only Lake Baikal,

38:31.080 --> 38:32.870
I will also take you to see

38:33.480 --> 38:35.090
every beautiful corner of the world.

38:43.160 --> 38:43.840
Lu Yan,

38:44.810 --> 38:46.700
we've really missed out on a lot.

38:48.400 --> 38:50.300
But fortunately, the ending is perfect.

39:04.970 --> 39:07.250
[Construction vehicle, Laowan District]

39:14.620 --> 39:18.080
[Analysis of Wen Peng's escape route]

40:01.270 --> 40:03.910
[Map of Ninghai City]

40:03.910 --> 40:08.360
[Construction vehicle, Laowan District, Nature Reserve]

40:14.360 --> 40:19.260
[Lu Yan, would you like to go to Lake Baikal with me in the future?]

40:35.710 --> 40:36.270
Lu Yan.

40:37.600 --> 40:38.540
Let me cover you up.

40:38.790 --> 40:39.710
Don't catch a cold at night.

41:04.600 --> 41:06.030
I'll sleep right next to you.

41:06.060 --> 41:07.190
You can call me if you need anything.
